      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/what-is-a-doula/" class="block bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-tjb-lavender-200 hover:border-tjb-rose-300 transition group">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-tjb-rose-500 transition">What Is a Doula?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray">The complete guide: what doulas do, what they don't do, and the three types.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/benefits-of-a-doula/" class="block bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-tjb-lavender-200 hover:border-tjb-rose-300 transition group">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-tjb-rose-500 transition">Benefits of a Doula</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray">The evidence: shorter labors, fewer interventions, higher satisfaction.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/faq/" class="block bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-tjb-lavender-200 hover:border-tjb-rose-300 transition group">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-tjb-rose-500 transition">Birth Plan FAQ</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray">Common questions about birth plans, doulas, and hospital policies answered.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>